nodes.text: Diala was a Human female who lived during the Galactic Civil War.

During 1 ABY, Diala resided in the city of Mos Espa on Tatooine. During this time, an individual named Barak tasked a smuggler with delivering a crate of contraband to Diala. The smuggler succeeded, despite having to dispatch a Mos Espa inspector.

Diala is a Non-Player Character (NPC) in the MMORPG Star Wars Galaxies. In the game, Barak gives quests to players who are in the smuggler profession, by having them deliver contraband to various NPC's. One of these NPC's is Diala.
